description: This file defines a data model for a national park adventure guide using Pydantic, sets up an agent with specific models, and executes a run to generate a park recommendation, printing the result.

classes.name: NationalParkAdventure
classes.description: A Pydantic data model representing detailed information about a national park adventure, including attractions, trails, wildlife, safety, and other features.

methods.name: Agent
methods.description: Constructor for creating an agent that can generate national park adventure guides.

methods.name: RunResponse
methods.description: A class representing the response from the agent's run method.
